subtype: Prize of the European Television Stations
title: DEUS EX MACHINA
Poster 1995
competition:
Paradoxically, the true graphic nature of William
Vance is that of a «Black and White painter» of
Nature. He loves to draw scenes usually
avoided by «normal» comic strip
artists: storms at sea during the
night, snow tempests, hurricanes,
torrential rains, volcano eruptions...
By the way, the monster drawn by
William Vance for the poster of the
13th Festival of Fantasy Film is not an
imaginary monster. It is a true monster
and its name is censorship.
